title: Kicking Off Week 4
description:
Wendi Nix, Desmond Howard and David Pollack discuss College Gameday and how Florida can slow down Tennessee's offense while having concerns with Anthony Richardson. Plus, hear from Shedeur Sanders as Tiffany Greene and Jay Walker highlight Jackson State and other HBCU colleges. Also, who does Desmond and David think will win the Big Ten West?
